a%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20smartphones%20and%20social%20media%20apps%20now%20track%20screen%20time%20and%20send%20reminders%20to%20close%20out%2C%20Elefante%20never%20uses%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20timers%20don't%20work%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20make%20me%20feel%20worse.%20I%20just%20snooze%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20one%20of%20her%20favorite%20hacks%20is%20only%20allowing%20herself%20to%20check%20Instagram%20once%20every%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20be%20OK%20with%20the%20idea%20that%20you're%20going%20to%20miss%20some%20potential%20contacts%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20since%20it's%20common%20for%20friends%20to%20share%20memes%20over%20social%20media%20DMs.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20Elefante%2C%20being%20slower%20to%20respond%20is%20a%20small%20price%20to%20pay%20for%20getting%20time%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fhow-to-break-social-media-addiction%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoff%20of%20the%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Make%20meaningful%20swaps%20for%20smartphones%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20why%20taking%20breaks%20from%20technology%20is%20so%20difficult%20is%20because%20it%20feels%20like%20you're%20taking%20something%20away%20instead%20of%20adding%20something%20new%2C%20Elefante%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20just%20create%20a%20vacuum%20where%20it%20was%20because%20you're%20going%20to%20spend%20your%20time%20feeling%20anxious%2C%20like%20you're%20missing%20out%20on%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20you%20have%20to%20put%20something%20in%20its%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElefante%20recommends%20making%20swaps%20like%20reading%20a%20physical%20book%20on%20your%20commute%20instead%20of%20on%20a%20tablet%20or%20doing%20crosswords%20with%20a%20pen%20and%20paper%20instead%20of%20playing%20online%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20picked%20up%20a%20camera%20again%2C%20an%20actual%20film%20camera%2C%20and%20started%20to%20go%20on%20walks%2C%26quot%3B%20Elefante%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20made%20it%20so%20I%20didn't%20feel%20stressed%20and%20anxious%20when%20I%20was%20without%20my%20phone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Get%20comfortable%20with%20saying%20no%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EElefante%20said%20that%20setting%20these%20boundaries%20can%20be%20hard%2C%20given%20how%20enticing%20social%20media%20is%20designed%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pull%20is%20very%2C%20very%20strong%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20it's%20a%20constant%20struggle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20keeps%20her%20focused%20on%20her%20goal%20is%20knowing%20what's%20most%20important%20to%20her.%20After%20accomplishing%20her%20dream%20of%20writing%20a%20book%2C%20she%20made%20compromises%20on%20how%20she%20would%20promote%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20said%20no%20to%20more%20things%20than%20you%20can%20possibly%20imagine%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-staying-off-phone-limiting-screen-time-cut-down-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704755177000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65987c2c1c5c7b8c9a0e8f61%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-staying-off-phone-limiting-screen-time-cut-down-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20media%20consultant%20experienced%20brain%20fog%20and%20memory%20loss%20from%20being%20online%20too%20much.%20She%20does%20these%204%20things%20to%20stay%20off%20her%20phone%20and%20limit%20her%20screen%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpugachevsky%40insider.com%20(Julia%20Pugachevsky)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessi