the%20letter%20have%20also%20been%20sent%20to%20Vice%20Chancellor%20Dr%20Ajmer%20Singh%20Malik%2C%20Haryana%20Governor%20Bandaru%20Dattatreya%2C%20Haryana%20Home%20Minister%20Anil%20Vij%2C%20and%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%20Chairperson%20Rekha%20Sharma%2C%20as%20well%20as%20senior%20state%20government%20officials%20and%20select%20media%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20accuses%20the%20professor%20of%20%26quot%3Bfilthy%20and%20obscene%20acts%26quot%3B.%20According%20to%20the%20letter%2C%20he%20calls%20girls%20to%20his%20office%2C%20takes%20them%20to%20a%20bathroom%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Btouches%20private%20parts%2C%20and%20(does)%20obscene%20things%20with%20us%26quot%3B.%20The%20girls%20said%20that%20when%20they%20protested%2C%20they%20were%20threatened%20with%20%26quot%3Bvery%20bad%26quot%3B%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20claims%20this%20has%20been%20going%20on%20%26quot%3Bfor%20many%20months%26quot%3B%20and%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20because%20he%20gives%20a%20false%20impression%20of%20a%20person%20of%20high%20character%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20professor%20in%20question%20has%20never%20been%20held%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20special%20investigation%20team%20(SIT)%20to%20probe%20the%20matter%2C%20police%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20immediately%20constituted%20the%20SIT%20under%20IPS%20officer%20Deepti%20Garg.%20(The%20SIT)%20is%20taking%20statements.%20It%20has%20already%20taken%20statements%20from%20many%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Additional%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20Shrikant%20Jadhav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SIT%20has%20already%20visited%20the%20university%20and%20statements%20are%20being%20taken%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20girls%20also%20claimed%20the%20Vice%20Chancellor%2C%20rather%20than%20come%20to%20their%20aid%2C%20%26quot%3Bthreatened%20to%20expel%20us...%20because%20this%20professor%20is%20a%20person%20of%20immense%20political%20influence...%26quot%3B%20The%20Vice%20Chancellor%20also%20reportedly%20tried%20to%20suppress%20the%20allegations%20by%20offering%20the%20girls%20better%20marks%20in%20written%20and%20practical%20examinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20university's%20Registrar%2C%20Dr%20Rajesh%20Kumar%20Bansal%2C%20confirmed%20receipt%20of%20the%20anonymous%20letter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20police%20are%20investigating...%20the%20university%20has%20its%20own%20committee%20which%20is%20probing%20the%20allegations.%20This%20is%20a%20serious%20accusation...%20there%20is%20no%20name%20on%20the%20letter%20but%20we%20will%20investigate%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAction%20will%20only%20be%20taken%20afterwards.%20Whoever%20is%20guilty%20will%20not%20be%20spared%20but%20if%20someone%20is%20innocent%20then%20their%20character%20should%20not%20be%20assassinated%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Registrar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Bansal%20said%20relevant%20CCTV%20footage%20had%20been%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20police.%20However%2C%20the%20letter%20claims%20the%20accused%20professor%20has%20already%20%26quot%3Bdeleted...%20his%20indecent%20actions%20from%20CCTV%20footage%20of%20his%20office%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20letter%20the%20girls%20-%20who%20said%20they%20had%20chosen%20not%20to%20reveal%20their%20identities%20fearing%20%26quot%3Bdishonour%26quot%3B%20to%20their%20famlies%20-%20said%20they%20do%20not%20expect%20action%20against%20the%20professor%20till%20the%20university%20is%20%26quot%3Bforced%26quot%3B%20by%20public%20opinion.%20The%20letter%20also%20calls%20for%20an%20investigation%20by%20a%20retired%20High%20Court%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F142-schoolgirls-allege-sexual-assault-by-principal-over-6-years-in-haryana-4597554%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E142%20Schoolgirls%20Allege%20Sexual%20Assault%20By%20Principal%20Over%206%20Years%20In%20Haryan