ail%20project%20between%20Ahmedabad%20and%20Mumbai%2C%20after%20a%20lengthy%20process.%20Railway%20minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20announced%20that%201%2C389.5%20hectares%20of%20land%20have%20been%20acquired%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20Dadra%20and%20Nagar%20Haveli.%20The%20National%20High%20Speed%20Rail%20Corporation%20Ltd%20(NHSRCL)%20has%20made%20progress%20in%20pier%20casting%20and%20girder%20launching%2C%20with%20the%20first%20trial%20run%20scheduled%20for%20August%202026.%20The%20government%20has%20maintained%20that%20the%20execution%20of%20the%20bullet%20train%20project%20has%20been%20impacted%20due%20to%20delay%20in%20land%20acquisition%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20consequent%20delays%20in%20finalisation%20of%20contracts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22DIPAK%20K%20DASH%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fbullet-train-project-gets-100-land-five-and-a-half-years-after-first-notification%2Farticleshow%2F106645749.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bilkis%20Bano%20Says%20%26quot%3BCan%20Breathe%20Again%26quot%3B%20After%20Supreme%20Court%20Verdict%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBilkis%20Bano%2C%20the%20survivor%20of%20one%20of%20the%20most%20horrific%20crimes%C2%A0%20during%20the%202002%20Gujarat%20riots%2C%20said%20today%20is%20%26quot%3Btruly%20the%20New%20Year%26quot%3B%20for%20her%20as%20the%2011%20men%20responsible%20for%20killing%20her%20family%20and%20gangraping%20her%20will%20soon%20be%20back%20behind%20the%20bars.%20Earlier%20today%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20that%20convicts%2C%20who%20got%20released%20last%20year%20for%20%26quot%3Bgood%20behaviour%26quot%3B%2C%20must%20return%20to%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20convicts%20have%20to%20surrender%20within%20two%20weeks%2C%20the%20top%20court%20said%2C%20declaring%20that%20the%20exercise%20of%20power%20by%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20was%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20application%20of%20mind%26quot%3B.%20The%20state%20was%20not%20competent%20to%20release%20the%20men%2C%20since%20only%20the%20state%20where%20the%20trial%20was%20held%20--%20in%20this%20case%20Maharashtra%20--%20is%20empowered%20to%20do%20this%2C%20the%20judges%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20wept%20tears%20of%20relief.%20I%20have%20smiled%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20over%20a%20year%20and%20half.%20I%20have%20hugged%20my%20children.%20It%20feels%20like%20a%20stone%20the%20size%20of%20a%20mountain%20has%20been%20lifted%20from%20my%20chest%2C%20and%20I%20can%20breathe%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20Nilkis%20Bano%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20issued%20through%20her%20lawyer%20Shobha%20Gupta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20what%20justice%20feels%20like.%20I%20thank%20the%20honourable%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20for%20giving%20me%2C%20my%20children%20and%20women%20everywhere%2C%20this%20vindication%20and%20hope%20in%20the%20promise%20of%20equal%20justice%20for%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20year%20and%20half%20ago%2C%20on%20August%2015%2C%202022%2C%20when%20those%20who%20had%20destroyed%20my%20family%20and%20terrorised%20my%20very%20existence%2C%20were%20given%20an%20early%20release%2C%20I%20simply%20collapsed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20To%20those%20who%20stood%20with%20her%20during%20that%20period%2C%20%26quot%3Bmy%20gratitude%20for%20your%20precious%20solidarity%20and%20strength%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20gave%20me%20the%20will%20to%20struggle%2C%20to%20rescue%20the%20idea%20of%20justice%20not%20just%20for%20me%2C%20but%20for%20every%20woman%20in%20India.%20I%20thank%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Bilkis%20Bano%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20as%20if%20a%20decision%20was%20made%20first%20and%20process%20applied%20later%2C%20and%20if%20i%20dare%20say%2C%20unmindfully%2C%26quot%3B%20remarked%20Shobha%20Gupta%2C%20who%20has%20been%20Bilkis%20Bano's%20legal%20counsel%20for%20decades.%20She%20also%20questioned%20the%20%26quot%3Bgood%20behaviour%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20men%20that%20was%20cited%20for%20their%20release.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20was%20the%20reflection%20of%20the%20good%20behaviour%3F%20Nothing%20was%20reflecting%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20men%20were%20released%20on%20Independence%20Day%20last%20year%20by%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20through%20an%20obsolete%20law%2C%20setting%20off%20a%20wave%20of%20outrage%20across%20the%20country.%20Bilkis%20Bano%20said%20she%20was%20was%20not%20informed%20about%20the%20release%20and%20expressed%20concern%20about%20the%20huge%20risk%20to%20her%20security%20it%20entailed.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnOnce%20out%2C%20the%20men%20received%20a%20hero's%20welcome%2C%20with%20sweets%20and%20garlands.%20Some%20of%20them%20were%20later%20spotted%20sharing%20stage%20with%20a%20BJP%20MP%20and%20MLA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20convict%20who%20made%20the%20initial%20petition%20for%20release%2C%20Radheshaym%20Shah%2C%20had%20even%20started%20practicing%20law%2C%20the%20top%20court%20was%20told%20during%20the%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704735360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-08%2F6v3e9to4_bilkis-bano-afp-650_625x300_17_August_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-year-for-me-bilkis-bano-on-big-supreme-court-order-4824420%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2011%20men%20responsible%20for%20killing%20her%20family%20and%20gangraping%20her%20soon%20to%20be%20back%20behind%20the%20bars%2C%20Bilkis%20Bano%20said%20today%20is%20%26quot%3Btruly%20the%20New%20Year%26quot%3B%20for%20her.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-year-for-me-bilkis-bano-on-big-supreme-court-order-4824420%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-year-for-me-bilkis-bano-on-big-supreme-court-order-4824420%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-year-for-me-bilkis-bano-on-big-supreme-court-order-4824420%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Today%2C%20I%20Can%20Breathe%20Again%2C%20Says%20Bilkis%20Bano%20After%20Landmark%20Supreme%20Court%20Judgement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08231538%2FBB.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Bilkis%20Bano%20smiled%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20today%2C%20she%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20thanking%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20its%20judgement%20undoing%20the%20remission%20given%20to%20those%20who%20raped%20her%20and%20murdered%20her%20family%20members%20during%20the%202002%20Gujarat%20riots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%20is%20truly%20the%20New%20Year%20for%20me.%20I%20have%20wept%20tears%20of%20relief.%20I%20have%20smiled%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20over%20a%20year%20and%20half.%20I%20have%20hugged%20my%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bano%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20issued%20through%20her%20lawyer%20Shobha%20Gupta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20two-judge%20division%20bench%20of%20the%20apex%20court%20said%20on%20Monday%20(January%208)%20that%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbilkis-bano-supreme-court-gujarat-not-competent-remission%5C%22%3Edid%20not%20have%20the%20power%20to%20grant%20premature%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%2011%20convicts%20who%20gang-raped%20a%20pregnant%20Bano%20and%20her%20family%20members%2C%20and%20also%20murdered%2014%20of%20her%20relatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20convicts%20had%20been%20sentenced%20to%20life%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20feels%20like%20a%20stone%20the%20size%20of%20a%20mountain%20has%20been%20lifted%20from%20my%20chest%2C%20and%20I%20can%20breathe%20again.%20This%20is%20what%20justice%20feels%20like%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bano%E2%80%99s%20letter%20continued%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20thank%20the%20honourable%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20for%20giving%20me%2C%20my%20children%20and%20women%20everywhere%2C%20this%20vindication%20and%20hope%20in%20the%20promise%20of%20equal%20justice%20for%20all.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20thanked%20her%20husband%20for%20children%20for%20staying%20by%20her%20side%20and%20her%20friends%20for%20%E2%80%9C%5Bholding%5D%20her%20hand%20at%20each%20difficult%20turn%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBano%20also%20thanked%20her%20lawyer%2C%20Gupta%2C%20saying%20she%20%E2%80%9Cnever%20allowed%20me%20to%20lose%20faith%20in%20the%20idea%20of%20justice%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20year%20and%20half%20ago%2C%20on%20August%2015%2C%202022%2C%20when%20those%20who%20had%20destroyed%20my%20family%20and%20terrorised%20my%20very%20existence%2C%20were%20given%20an%20early%20release%2C%20I%20simply%20collapsed%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20felt%20I%20had%20exhausted%20my%20reservoir%20of%20courage.%20Until%20a%20million%20solidarities%20came%20my%20way.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20ordinary%20people%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20wrote%20appeals%20and%20open%20letters%20in%20solidarity%20with%20her%2C%20Bano%20said%2C%20saying%20they%20had%20given%20every%20woman%20in%20India%20the%20will%20to%20%E2%80%9Crescue%20the%20idea%20of%20justice%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGujarat%E2%80%99s%20government%20said%20the%20decision%20to%20remit%20the%20convicts%E2%80%99%20sentence%20was%20arrived%20at%20by%20a%20panel%20it%20had%20set%20up%2C%20comprising%20officials%20and%20%E2%80%98social%20workers%E2%80%99%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20were%20either%20members%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20or%20were%20connected%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20division%20bench%20comprising%20Justices%20B.V.%20Nagarathna%20and%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%20said%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20%E2%80%9Cacted%20in%20complicity%20with%20the%20convicts%E2%80%9D%20and%20noted%20that%20if%20the%20convicts%20can%20%E2%80%9Ccircumvent%20the%20consequences%20of%20their%20conviction%2C%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20in%20the%20society%20will%20be%20reduced%20to%20a%20chimaera.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBano%20said%20the%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20decision%20affirmed%20her%20belief%20in%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20as%20I%20absorb%20the%20full%20meaning%20of%20this%20verdict%20for%20my%20own%20life%2C%20and%20for%20my%20children%E2%80%99s%20lives%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Edua%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20emerges%20from%20my%20heart%20today%20is%20simple%20%E2%80%93%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20above%20all%20else%20and%20equality%20before%20law%2C%20for%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20full%20statement%2C%20which%20was%20also%20issued%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20Hindi%2C%20is%20reproduced%20below%20in%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBilkis%20Yakub%20Rasool%E2%80%99s%20Statement%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJanuary%208%2C%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20of%20Justice%20B.V.%20Nagarathna%20and%20Justice%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%20quashed%20the%20remission%20granted%20to%20the%2011%20men%20convicted%20of%20gang-raping%20Bilkis%20Bano%20and%20murdering%2014%20members%20of%20her%20family%20in%202002%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%20is%20truly%20the%20New%20Year%20for%20me.%20I%20have%20wept%20tears%20of%20relief.%20I%20have%20smiled%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20over%20a%20year%20and%20half.%20I%20have%20hugged%20my%20children.%20It%20feels%20like%20a%20stone%20the%20size%20of%20a%20mountain%20has%20been%20lifted%20from%20my%20chest%2C%20and%20I%20can%20breathe%20again.%20This%20is%20what%20justice%20feels%20like.%20I%20thank%20the%20honourable%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20for%20giving%20me%2C%20my%20children%20and%20women%20everywhere%2C%20this%20vindication%20and%20hope%20in%20the%20promise%20of%20equal%20justice%2