6quot%3BThe%20bridge%20was%20built%20following%20all%20rules%20after%20obtaining%20NOC%20from%20the%20Railways%20and%20Defence%20ministries%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Yadav%2C%20who%20had%20dedicated%20the%20bridge%20to%20the%20public%20in%202014%20when%20he%20was%20the%20then%20chief%20minister%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20BSP%20chief's%20request%20to%20shift%20her%20party%20office%20because%20of%20security%20concerns%2C%20the%20SP%20president%20retorted%2C%20%26quot%3BWho%20has%20stopped%20them%2C%20they%20are%20hand-in-glove%20with%20the%20BJP.%20If%20the%20BSP%20leadership%20feels%20that%20its%20security%20is%20in%20danger%20then%20it%20should%20write%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Central%20government%20and%20get%20this%20bridge%20demolished.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20government%20has%20many%20bulldozers%20and%20can%20bring%20it%20down.%20I%20am%20prepared%20for%20it%20if%20the%20BJP%20listens%20to%20Mayawati%20ji%2C%20we%20have%20no%20complaints%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20further%20said%20former%20chief%20minister%20N%20D%20Tiwari%20used%20to%20take%20keen%20interest%20when%20it%20was%20being%20constructed%20and%20was%20also%20present%20at%20its%20inauguration.%20%26quot%3BWill%20they%20blame%20ND%20Tiwari%20also%3F%20Who%20all%20will%20be%20blamed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Keshav%20Prasad%20Maurya%20took%20a%20jibe%20at%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20following%20Mayawati's%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBSP%20chief%20Ms%20Mayawati's%20doubt%20on%20the%20SP%20regarding%20her%20security%20proves%20that%20the%20character%20of%20the%20SP%20has%20still%20not%20changed.%20The%20SP%20government%20had%20made%20a%20nefarious%20attempt%20to%20murder%20Behen%20Mayawati%20in%20the%20guest%20house%20incident.%20The%20government%20has%20always%20been%20alert%20regarding%20the%20safety%20of%20Mayawati%20and%20the%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20of%20the%20previous%20SP%20government%20had%20generated%20much%20heat%20as%20the%20BSP%20leaders%20had%20vehemently%20protested%20against%20its%20construction%2C%20alleging%20that%20it%20was%20a%20security%20threat%20to%20Mayawati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20had%20alleged%20that%20the%20over%20bridge%20posed%20a%20threat%20by%20exposing%20Mayawati's%20bungalow%20at%20Mall%20Avenue%20as%20well%20as%20the%20BSP%20office%20in%20Lucknow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMayawati%20said%20that%20the%20BSP%20had%20to%20shift%20the%20statues%20of%20many%20personalities%20to%20her%20residence%20due%20to%20security%20problems%2C%20adding%20that%20given%20the%20insecurity%2C%20the%20party%20had%20to%20shift%20important%20meetings%20from%20the%20party%20office%20to%20her%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSP%20chief%20said%20that%20this%20would%20also%20help%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20deal%20strictly%20with%20the%20anti-Dalit%20elements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BSP%20makes%20a%20special%20request%20to%20the%20UP%20government%20to%20make%20arrangements%20at%20a%20safe%20place%20somewhere%20else%20instead%20of%20the%20current%20party%20state%20office%20otherwise%20any%20untoward%20incident%20can%20happen%20here%20at%20any%20time.%20Besides%2C%20the%20party%20also%20demands%20that%20the%20government%20should%20deal%20strictly%20with%20anti-Dalit%20elements%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20series%20of%20tweets%20earlier%20in%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20requesting%20for%20her%20party%20office%20to%20be%20shifted%2C%20Mayawati%20recalled%20the%20unpleasant%20incident%20of%201995.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20guest%20house%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20June%202%2C%201995%2C%20when%20Mayawati%20had%20withdrawn%20support%20from%20the%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav-led%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agitated%20Samajwadi%20Party%