ace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20administration%20of%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20will%20release%20a%20final%20rule%20as%20soon%20as%20this%20week%20that%20will%20make%20it%20more%20difficult%20for%20companies%20to%20treat%20workers%20as%20independent%20contractors%20rather%20than%20employees%20that%20typically%20cost%20a%20company%20more%2C%20an%20administration%20official%20said.%20The%20US%20Department%20of%20Labor%20rule%2C%20which%20was%20first%20proposed%20in%202022%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20face%20legal%20challenges%2C%20will%20require%20that%20workers%20be%20considered%20employees%20entitled%20to%20more%20benefits%20and%20legal%20protections%20than%20contractors%20when%20they%20are%20%26quot%3Beconomically%20dependent%26quot%3B%20on%20a%20company.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjoe-biden-administration-to-announce-independent-contractor-rule-that-could-upend-gig-economy%2Farticleshow%2F106644333.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjoe-biden-administration-to-announce-independent-contractor-rule-that-could-upend-gig-economy%2Famp_articleshow%2F106644333.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjoe-biden-administration-to-announce-independent-contractor-rule-that-could-upend-gig-economy%2Famp_articleshow%2F106644333.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWrite%20In%20Capital%20Letters%26quot%3B%3A%20High%20Court%20On%20Doctors'%20%26quot%3BZigzag%20Handwriting%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Orissa%20High%20Court%20has%20directed%20the%20state%20government%20to%20issue%20a%20circular%20asking%20doctors%20to%20write%20all%20prescriptions%20and%20medico-legal%20reports%20in%20legible%20handwriting%2C%20if%20possible%2C%20in%20capital%20letters%20or%20in%20a%20typed%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20ensure%20that%20the%20judicial%20system%20does%20not%20suffer%20from%20%26quot%3Bunnecessary%20fatigue%26quot%3B%20in%20reading%20those%20documents%2C%20the%20order%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20direction%20came%20from%20the%20High%20Court%20last%20week%20when%20Justice%20S%20K%20Panigrahi%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20decide%20a%20case%2C%20as%20the%20post-mortem%20examination%20report%20annexed%20in%20the%20petition%20was%20not%20legible%20and%20could%20not%20be%20comprehended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20petitioner%20had%20approached%20the%20court%20seeking%20a%20direction%20to%20the%20government%20to%20consider%20his%20representation%20for%20ex-gratia%20assistance%20as%20his%20elder%20son%20had%20died%20due%20to%20snakebite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20compliance%20with%20an%20earlier%20order%2C%20the%20doctor%20who%20had%20written%20the%20post-mortem%20examination%20report%20appeared%20before%20the%20court%20through%20virtual%20mode%2C%20read%20out%20the%20incomprehensible%20document%20and%20rendered%20his%20opinion.%20Following%20this%2C%20the%20court%20was%20able%20to%20realise%20that%20it%20was%20a%20snakebite%20case%20and%20adjudicated%20over%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20many%20cases%2C%20the%20casual%20approach%20of%20most%20of%20the%20doctors%20while%20writing%20the%20post-mortem%20reports%2C%20is%20affecting%20comprehension%20of%20medico-legal%20cases%20very%20badly%2C%20and%20the%20judicial%20system%20finds%20it%20very%20difficult%20to%20read%20those%20(reports)%20to%20come%20to%20a%20definite%20conclusion%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Panigrahi%20observed%20in%20his%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20tendency%20of%20writing%20such%20%26quot%3Bzigzag%20handwriting%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20cannot%20be%20read%20by%20a%20common%20man%20or%20judicial%20officers%2C%20has%20become%20a%20fashion%20among%20the%20doctors%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHence%2C%20this%20court%20directs%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%2C%20State%20of%20Odisha%2C%20to%20issue%20directions%20to%20all%20doctors%20of%20the%20state%20to%20write%20post-mortem%20reports%20and%20prescriptions%20in%20capital%20letters%20or%20in%20legible%20handwriting%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20high%20court%20said%20in%20the%20order%20passed%20on%20January%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704727320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fuf97do2_doctor-generic-unsplash_625x300_16_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwrite-prescriptions-in-legible-handwriting-orrisa-high-court-tells-doctors-4823938%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Orissa%20High%20Court%20has%20directed%20the%20state%20government%20to%20issue%20a%20circular%20asking%20doctors%20to%20write%20all%20prescriptions%20and%20medico-legal%20reports%20in%20legible%20handwriting%2C%20if%20possible%2C%20in%20capital%20letters%20or%20in%20a%20typed%20form.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwrite-prescriptions-in-legible-handwriting-orrisa-high-court-tells-doctors-4823938%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwrite-prescriptions-in-legible-handwriting-orrisa-high-court-tells-doctors-4823938%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwrite-prescriptions-in-legible-handwriting-orrisa-high-court-tells-doctors-4823938%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blackstone's%20first%20private%20equity%20fund%20for%20rich%20individuals%20gets%20%241.3%20bn%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704727213000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-01%2F08%2Ffull%2F1704727127-0943.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fblackstone-s-first-private-equity-fund-for-rich-individuals-gets-1-3-bn-124010801173_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20cash%20pile%2C%20disclosed%20in%20a%20filing%20Monday%2C%20underscores%20the%20intensifying%20race%20among%20alternative%20investment%20firms%20to%20court%20private%20wealth%20as%20key%20sources%20of%20institutional%20money%20dry%20up%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fblackstone-s-first-private-equity-fund-for-rich-individuals-gets-1-3-bn-124010801173_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fblackstone-s-first-private-equity-fund-for-rich-individuals-gets-1-3-bn-124010801173_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fblackstone-s-first-private-equity-fund-for-rich-individuals-gets-1-3-bn-124010801173_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20Ex%20Diplomat%20Details%20What%20Led%20To%20Agra%20Summit%20Collapse%20In%202001%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20then%20President%20Pervez%20Musharraf's%20%26quot%3Boverreach%26quot%3B%20in%20publicly%20airing%20his%20hawkish%20views%20on%20Kashmir%2C%20his%20lack%20of%20intent%20in%20containing%20terrorism%20and%20insistence%20on%20a%20formulation%20linking%20forward%20movement%20in%20overall%20ties%20to%20progress%20on%20Kashmir%20led%20to%20the%20collapse%20of%20Agra%20Summit%20in%202001%20and%20not%20because%20of%20LK%20Advani's%20hardline%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20Ambassador%20Ajay%20Bisaria%2C%20who%20served%20as%20a%20key%20aide%20of%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20when%20he%20was%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20said%20in%20his%20upcoming%20book%20while%20throwing%20light%20on%20various%20dramatic%20details%20of%20the%20historic%20Agra%20Summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20second%20day%20of%20the%20Summit%2C%20Musharraf%20met%20with%20editors%20of%20major%20newspapers%20and%20TV%20networks%20for%20a%20breakfast%20conversation%20during%20which%20he%20%26quot%3Blet%20loose%26quot%3B%20his%20hawkish%20position%20on%20Kashmir%20and%20equated%20terrorists%20with%20freedom%20fighters%2C%20Mr%20Bisaria%20recounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20book%2C%20'Anger%20Management%3A%20The%20Troubled%20Diplomatic%20Relationship%20Between%20India%20and%20Pakistan'%2C%20Mr%20Bisaria%20says%20this%20public%20telecast%20sounded%20to%20observers%20like%20a%20mid-summit%20report%20on%20the%20talks%2C%20where%20Pakistan's%20hard%20views%20were%20being%20inflicted%20on%20India%2C%20while%20New%20Delhi's%20positions%20were%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20diplomat%20says%20he%20and%20Brajesh%20Mishra%2C%20Vajpayee's%20principal%20secretary%20and%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20from%201998%20to%202004%2C%20watched%20Musharraf's%20televised%20remarks%20with%20%26quot%3Bdismay%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20makeshift%20PMO%20in%20Agra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMishra%20turned%20to%20me%20and%20said%20that%20the%20PM%20needed%20to%20be%20informed%20of%20this%20development%2C%20since%20he%20was%20sitting%20in%20conversation%20with%20Musharraf%20oblivious%20to%20everything%20happening%20outside%20the%20meeting%20room.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BMishra%20scribbled%20a%20few%20lines.%20I%20had%20them%20quickly%20typed%20up%2C%20adding%20a%20couple%20of%20sentences%20of%20my%20own.%20The%20note%20basically%20said%20that%20a%20press%20conference%20by%20Musharraf%20was%20being%20telecast%2C%20where%20he%20had%20repeated%20his%20hardline%20positions%2C%20harping%20on%20the%20Kashmir%20issue%20and%20had%20talked%20of%20terrorists%20as%20freedom%20fighters%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bisaria%20writes%20in%20the%20book%20being%20published%20by%20Rupa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20fell%20upon%20Mr%20Bisaria%20to%20walk%20into%20the%20room%20where%20the%20two%20leaders%20and%20the%20two%20notetakers%20were%20sitting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20arrival%20interrupted%20the%20conversation%20as%20both%20leaders%20looked%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMusharraf%20had%20been%20talking%20and%20Vajpayee%20was%20listening%2C%20apparently%20with%20great%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20handed%20over%20the%20paper%20to%20the%20boss%20and%20said%20that%20there%20had%20been%20some%20important%20developments.%20After%20I%20left%20the%20room%2C%20Vajpayee%20looked%20at%20the%20paper%20and%20then%20read%20out%20from%20it%20to%20Musharraf%2C%20saying%20edgily%20that%20his%20behaviour%20was%20not%20helping%20the%20talks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bisaria%20says%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bplayfully%26quot%3B%20accused%20by%20some%20colleagues%20of%20torpedoing%20the%20Agra%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20diplomat%20further%20says%20the%20narrative%20that%20emerged%20from%20the%20meetings%20in%20view%20of%20Pakistani%20leaks%20was%20that%20while%20Vajpayee%20and%20Foreign%20Minister%20Jaswant%20Singh%20were%20for%20an%20understanding%20and%20%26quot%3BOK%26quot%3B%20with%20Pakistan's%20%26quot%3Bconvoluted%20draft%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Agra%20joint%20statement%20(linking%20progress%20in%20bilateral%20ties%20to%20forward%20movement%20on%20the%20Kashmir%20issue)%2C%20Advani%2C%20the%20hawk%2C%20had%20vetoed%20it%20since%20he%20did%20not%20want%20any%20progress%20with%20Islamabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdvani%20was%20quite%20aware%20of%20the%20slant%20in%20the%20media%20reporting%2C%20making%20him%20the%20villain%20of%20the%20piece.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BLater%20Pakistani%20writings%20tend%20to%20highlight%20the%20almost%20agreed%20upon%20draft.%20The%20reality%20was%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bisaria%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bisaria%2C%20who%20retired%20from%20foreign%20service%20in%20June%202022%2C%20also%20referred%20to%20Jaswant%20Singh's%20talks%20with%20then%20Pakistan%20Foreign%20Minister%20Abdul%20Sattar%20on%20the%20draft%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJaswant%20Singh%20walked%20into%20Vajpayee's%20hotel%20suite%20to%20show%20him%20the%20paper%20he%20had%20negotiated%20with%20his%20counterpart%2C%20Sattar.%20Vajpayee%20asked%20his%20other%20cabinet%20colleagues%20to%20come%20to%20the%20suite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBrajesh%20Mishra%20was%20already%20present%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPakistan's%20initial%20formulations%20linking%20a%20Kashmir%20settlement%20to%20other%20bilateral%20matters%20had%20been%20diluted%2C%20but%20the%20first%20operative%20paragraph%20still%20referred%20to%20'progress%20towards%20settlement%20of%20(the)%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20issue.'%20The%20draft%20ended%20with%20calling%20for%20addressing%20all%20issues%20'in%20an%20integrated%20manner.'%20%26quot%3BThe%20draft%20also%20asked%20for%20a%20sustained%20dialogue%20at%20the%20political%20level%20on%20terrorism%2C%20but%20made%20no%20promises%20of%20Pakistan%20curtailing%20it.%20While%20the%20overall%20formulations%20seemed%20innocent%20enough%2C%20the%20draft%20was%20sending%20a%20political%20message%20that%20India%20was%20letting%20Musharraf%20get%20away%20lightly%20on%20the%20terrorism%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeveral%20red%20flags%20went%20up%20in%20the%20room.%26quot%3B%20In%20the%20book%2C%20Mr%20Bisaria%20says%20that%20Jaswant%20Singh%20recalled%20the%20%26quot%3B'collective%20view%20expressed%20there%20was%20that%20without%20sufficient%20and%20clear%20emphasis%20on%20terrorism%2C%20also%20accepting%20categorically%20that%20it%20must%20cease%2C%20how%20could%20there%20be%20any%20significant%20movement%20on%20issues%20that%20are%20of%20concern%20or%20are%20a%20priority%20only%20to%20Pakistan%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B'And%20none%20that%20are%20in%20the%20hierarchy%20of%20priorities%20for%20India%3F%20How%20can%20we%20abandon%20Shimla%20or%20Lahore%3F%20Or%20forget%20the%20reality%20of%20Kargil%3F%20I%20went%20back%20and%20reported%20failure%20to%20Sattar'%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bisaria%20writes%20quoting%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20Jaswant%20Singh%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20room%2C%20Advani%20sighed%20and%20said%2C%20in%20English%2C%20that%20he%20would%20now%20be%20the%20'fall%20guy'%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvani%20was%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20at%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bisaria%20notes%20in%20the%20book%20that%20%26quot%3BMusharraf's%20overreach%20in%20terms%20of%20publicly%20broadcasting%20hawkish%20positions%20on%20Kashmir--%20and%20his%20insistence%20on%20a%20formulation%20linking%20progress%20on%20all%20issues%20with%20progress%20on%20Kashmir%20--%20had%20led%20to%20the%20unravelling%20of%20the%20summit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20another%20factor%20was%20that%20both%20countries%20attempted%20to%20summit%20a%20mountain%20with%20little%20planning%20or%20even%20Sherpas%20to%20help%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNegotiating%20a%20joint%20statement%20at%20the%20level%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20foreign%20minister%20was%20not%20the%20smartest%20choice%20by%20Pakistan%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20had%20been%20little%20diplomatic%20bargaining%2C%20no%20backchannel%20dialogue%2C%20and%20limited%20diplomatic%20attempts%20to%20choreograph%20the%20Summit's%20outcomes%20to%20bridge%20the%20vast%20chasm%20in%20the%20two%20positions%20on%20Kashmir%20and%20terrorism%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bisaria%20also%20recounts%20his%20conversation%20with%20Vajpayee%20and%20Brajesh%20Mishra%20months%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20India%20had%20gone%20with%20a%20bland%20text%20to%20declare%20the%20Summit%20a%20success%20and%20then%20cross-border%20terrorism%20had%20continued%2C%20would%20we%20not%20have%20appeared%20even%20more%20gullible%20than%20we%20did%20when%20the%20Summit%20was%20declared%20a%20failure%3F%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BMishra%20agreed%20that%20would%20have%20been%20a%20worse%20outcome.%26quot%3B%20Bisaria%20adds%3A%20%26quot%3BStill%2C%20the%20invitation%20to%20Musharraf%20served%20a%20purpose%2C%20Vajpayee%20did%20manage%20to%20read%20Pakistan's%20loquacious%20dictator%2C%20and%20this%20experience%20would%20help%20him%20evolve%20his%20Pakistan%20policy%20over%20the%20next%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Summit%20did%20not%20succeed%2C%20but%20diplomacy%20had%20worked.%20It%20had%20worked%20for%20both%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704727020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-11%2Fethqm5pg_agra-summit-afp-650_625x300_28_November_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fagra-summit-collapsed-due-to-musharrafs-kashmir-overreach-lack-of-intent-to-combat-terror-not-because-of-advani-book-4823748%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan's%20then%20President%20Pervez%20Musharraf's%20%26quot%3Boverreach%26quot%3B%20in%20publicly%20airing%20his%20hawkish%20views%20on%20Kashmir%2C%20his%20lack%20of%20intent%20in%20containing%20terrorism%20led%20to%20the%20collapse%20of%20Agra%20Summit%20in%202001%20and%20not%20because%20of%20LK%20Advani's%20hardline%20approach.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fagra-summit-collapsed-due-to-musharrafs-kashmir-overreach-lack-of-intent-to-combat-terror-not-because-of-advani-book-4823748%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fagra-summit-collapsed-due-to-musharrafs-kashmir-overreach-lack-of-intent-to-combat-terror-not-because-of-advani-book-4823748%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22