%20included%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sandeep%20Pathak%2C%20Delhi%20minister%20Atishi%20and%20MLA%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20reporters%20after%20the%20meeting%2C%20Wasnik%20said%20that%20discussions%20were%20held%20on%20seat%20sharing%20as%20well%20as%20various%20other%20aspects%20of%20the%20upcoming%20elections%2C%20and%20that%20a%20final%20decision%20will%20be%20taken%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20a%20very%20good%20meeting.%20Senior%20AAP%20leaders%20were%20sent%20to%20today%E2%80%99s%20meeting%20for%20holding%20discussions%20with%20us%20on%20behalf%20of%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%20The%20National%20Alliance%20Committee%20formed%20by%20the%20Congress%20president%20held%20discussions%20with%20AAP%20leaders%20for%20about%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20on%20different%20issues%20relating%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20seats%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20decided%20to%20hold%20further%20discussions%20and%20a%20final%20decision%20will%20be%20taken%20in%20the%20upcoming%20days.%20Discussion%20covered%20various%20issues.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWasnik%20did%20not%2C%20however%2C%20divulge%20details%20on%20any%20seat-sharing%20agreements%20that%20were%20reached%20or%20the%20seats%20that%20were%20under%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20proper%20to%20reveal%20what%20transpired%20during%20the%20discussions.%20You%20will%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20some%20time.%20We%20have%20already%20decided%20to%20contest%20elections%20together.%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20are%20a%20strong%20and%20important%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Lovely%20said%20that%20the%20discussion%20was%20%E2%80%9Cpositive%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cpreliminary%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20only%20a%20preliminary%20meeting%20today%20and%20the%20seat%20sharing%20will%20be%20discuss