gnihotri-roots-for-india-tourism-as-he-highlights-the-beauty-and-magnificence-of-indian-beaches-and-islands-see-photos%2Farticleshow%2F106642527.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Tech%20Valuations%20Put%20To%20The%20Test%20As%20Earnings%20Remain%20Under%20Pressure%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20IT%20services%20giants%20may%20struggle%20to%20justify%20their%20valuations%20when%20they%20kick%20off%20Asia's%20reporting%20season%20this%20week%2C%20as%20earnings%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20the%20weakest%20in%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20tech%20sector%20index%2C%20which%20includes%20Infosys%20Ltd.%20and%20Tata%20Consultancy%20Services%20Ltd.%2C%20rallied%2012%25%20in%20the%20three%20months%20through%20December%2C%20powered%20by%20a%20global%20rally%20in%20the%20space%20after%20a%20dovish%20pivot%20by%20the%20Federal%20Reserve.%20India's%20tech%20stocks%20trade%20at%20about%20a%2027%25%20premium%20to%20the%20broader%20market.%20Improved%20sentiment%20aside%2C%20IT%20earnings%20remain%20under%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20sentiment%20has%20improved%2C%20it%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20reflected%20in%20actions%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mukul%20Garg%20and%20Pritesh%20Thakkar%2C%20analysts%20at%20Motilal%20Oswal%20Financial%20Services.%20Analysts%20at%20Nomura%20expect%20the%20ongoing%20slowdown%20to%20weigh%20on%20discretionary%20tech%20spending%20into%20the%202025%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirms%20in%20the%20sector%20are%20focused%20on%20integrating%20generative%20AI%20into%20their%20operations%20and%20training%20employees%20to%20use%20the%20tool%20effectively.%20Earnings%20at%20Samsung%20Electronics%20Co.%2C%20which%20is%20set%20to%20benefit%20from%20AI%20chip%20demand%20this%20year%2C%20found%20support%20from%20higher%20shipments%20of%20DRAM%20chips%20during%20the%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHighlights%20to%20look%20out%20for%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETuesday%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESamsung%20Electronics'%20(005930%20KS)%20bit%20shipments%20for%20DRAM%20may%20have%20grown%20with%20higher%20average%20selling%20prices%2C%20Bloomberg%20Intelligence%20said.%20NAND%20sales%20probably%20also%20increased%2C%20though%20average%20selling%20prices%20remain%20weak.%20Overall%2C%20fourth-quarter%20revenue%20was%20probably%20steady%2C%20while%20net%20income%20fell.%20HSBC%20analysts%20including%20Ricky%20Seo%20expect%20slight%20margin%20pressure%20on%20smartphones%20from%20rising%20marketing%20costs%20and%20OLED.%20The%20company%20targets%20operating%20profit%20of%2011.5%20trillion%20won%20(%248.8%20billion)%20in%20the%20chip%20business%20in%202024%2C%20driven%20by%20the%20rebound%20in%20DRAM%20prices%20and%20revived%20chip%20demand%20on%20AI%2C%20the%20Korea%20Economic%20Daily%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThursday%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Tata%20Consultancy%20Services%20(TCS%20IN)%20is%20poised%20to%20report%20its%20weakest%20quarterly%20revenue%20growth%20since%20July-Sept.%202020%20on%20cuts%20in%20discretionary%20tech%20spending%20by%20its%20US%20and%20European%20clients.%20The%20firm%2C%20which%20has%20consistently%20delivered%20double-digit%20revenue%20growth%20for%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20is%20forecast%20for%20just%203.2%25%20revenue%20growth%2C%20Bloomberg%20consensus%20estimates%20show.%20Ramp-ups%20of%20larger%20deals%2C%20including%20one%20with%20state-owned%20telecommunications%20giant%20BSNL%2C%20helped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfosys%20(INFO%20IN)%20may%20report%20its%20first%20quarterly%20profit%20drop%20since%20July-Sept.%202019%20as%20seasonal%20furloughs%20coincided%20with%20the%20slowdown%20in%20discretionary%20tech%20spending.%20Revenue%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20little%20changed%2C%20with%20inflows%20from%20the%20telecommunications%20and%20finance%20sectors%20hit%20the%20hardest.%20Infosys%2C%20a%20major%20employer%20for%20the%20nation's%20engineering%20graduates%2C%20shook%20markets%20last%20quarter%20after%20it%20said%20it%20had%20paused%20hiring%20to%20cut%20costs.%20Still%2C%20BNP%20Paribas%20analyst%20Kumar%20Rakesh%20said%20large%20firms%20with%20strong%20client%20relationships%20will%20fare%20better%20in%20the%20current%20climate%2C%20with%20Infosys%20a%20top%20pick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20Retailing's%20(9983%20JP)%20first-quarter%20operating%20profit%20probably%20increased%2C%20but%20Uniqlo's%20margin%20growth%20may%20have%20slowed%20sequentially%20on%20higher%20labor%20costs%20and%20store%20expansion%20expenses%2C%20BI%20said%20in%20a%20post-earnings%20note%20on%20Oct.%2013.%20A%20warmer%20winter%20than%20usual%20may%20also%20have%20hit%20sales%20of%20autumn-winter%20clothing%20in%20Japan%2C%20they%20added.%20Analysts%20at%20SMBC%20Nikko%20expect%20Uniqlo's%20international%20business%20to%20drive%20earnings%20growth%20in%20the%20medium%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFriday%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20HDFC%20Life%20Insurance%20(HDFCLIFE%20IN)%20will%20report%20profit%20falling%20by%20more%20than%20half%20as%20it%20struggles%20to%20gain%20market%20share.%20Analysts%20at%20Nirmal%20Bang%20Institutional%20Equities%20also%20expect%20HDFC%20Life%20to%20be%20especially%20impacted%20by%20a%20new%20draft%20regulation%20on%20policy%20surrender%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704720660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F0j4ettd4_office-generic-bloomberg_625x300_08_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-tech-valuations-put-to-the-test-as-earnings-remain-under-pressure-4823552%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20IT%20services%20giants%20may%20struggle%20to%20justify%20their%20valuations%20when%20they%20kick%20off%20Asia's%20reporting%20season%20this%20week%2C%