y%20Vidhu%20Vinod%20Chopra%2C%20'12th%20Fail'%20revolves%20around%20UPSC%20aspirants%20and%20portrays%20the%20challenges%20they%20face.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvikrant-massey-reacts-as-rohit-shetty-meets-real-hero-of-12th-fail-ips-manoj-kumar-sharma-see-photo%2Farticleshow%2F106642025.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inter-Faith%20Cousins%20Thrashed%20For%20Hours%20By%20Mob%20In%20Karnataka%20Horror%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20shocking%20case%20of%20moral%20policing%2C%20a%20man%20and%20woman%20from%20different%20communities%20were%20brutally%20thrashed%20with%20pipes%20and%20rods%20by%20a%20group%20of%2017%20people%20for%20sitting%20together%20near%20a%20lake%20in%20Karnataka's%20Belagavi%20Saturday.%20The%20victims%20happen%20to%20be%20cousins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20out%20together%20to%20apply%20for%20the%20state%20government's%20scheme%20but%20were%20assaulted%20for%20hours%20till%20their%20families%20came%20to%20their%20rescue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20belonged%20to%20a%20minority%20community%2C%20police%20said%2C%20adding%20nine%20of%20them%20have%20been%20arrested.%20Two%20of%20them%20are%20juveniles%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victims%20were%20sitting%20near%20Killa%20Lake%20in%20Belagavi%20at%20around%201%3A30%20PM%20on%20Saturday%20when%20a%20group%20of%20around%20eight%20approached%20them%20and%20started%20asking%20for%20their%20names.%20When%20they%20learned%20that%20they%20were%20from%20different%20religions%2C%20they%20started%20questioning%20him%20as%20to%20why%20he%20was%20sitting%20next%20to%20the%20woman%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20goons%20abused%20the%20man%20and%20even%20tried%20to%20strangle%20him%2C%20according%20to%20the%20complaint.%20Subsequently%2C%20more%20people%20joined%20the%20group%20and%20they%20took%20the%20cousins%20to%20a%20room%20and%20brutally%20thrashed%20the%20man%20for%20hours%2C%20as%20per%20the%20complaint.%20They%20thrashed%20him%20till%206%3A30%20PM%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20was%20also%20attacked%2C%20according%20to%20police%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20alleged%20that%20the%20mob%20took%20their%20mobile%20phones%20away%20and%20also%20robbed%20cash%20from%20them.%20%26quot%3BThey%20asked%20why%20people%20from%20different%20communities%20were%20sitting%20together.%20I%20told%20them%20she%20was%20my%20own%20aunt's%20daughter.%20They%20took%20our%20phones.%20They%20took%20Rs%207%2C000%20cash%20from%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman's%20parents%20belong%20to%20different%20religions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20man%20was%20from%20a%20Scheduled%20Castes%20community%2C%20a%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Atrocities%20Act%2C%20said%20police%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20has%20elicited%20reactions%20from%20state%20political%20leaders%20who%20called%20such%20incidents%20a%20%26quot%3Bsocial%20issue%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20told%20they%20were%20relatives%20and%20that%20they%20were%20just%20sitting%20and%20chatting%20when%20suddenly%20this%20group%20approached%20them.%20Police%20have%20already%20made%20some%20arrests.%20We%20handle%20these%20(cases%20of%20moral%20policing%20based%20on%20communities%20or%20caste)%20on%20a%20case-by-case%20basis.%20These%20things%20don't%20always%20happen.%20Police%20take%20action%20accordingly.%20Each%20case%20is%20different.%20Sometimes%20youngsters%20are%20involved%2C%20sometimes%20elders%20are%20involved%20and%20sometimes%20family%20members%20are%20involved.%20We%20can't%20predict%20(these%20cases)%2C%20Karnataka%20Home%20Minister%20G%20Parameshwara%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20issue%20of%20opposition%20faced%20by%20inter-faith%20couples%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20social%20problem.%20Basavanna%20(a%2012th-century%20poet%20and%20philosopher)%20had%20advocated%20for%20inter-community%20weddings%20because%20he%20wanted%20a%20caste-less%20society.%20As%20a%20social%20problem%2C%20this%20has%20to%20be%20resolved%20gradually.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP's%20CN%20Ashwath%20Narayan%20said%20that%20the%20public%20%26quot%3Bshouldn't%20take%20the%20law%20into%20their%20hands%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20someone%20has%20any%20doubts%20about%20someone's%20intention%2C%20they%20should%20call%20the%20concerned%20authorities%20and%20let%20them%20be%20enquired%20by%20the%20authorities.%20People%20shouldn't%20take%20the%20law%20into%20their%20hands.%20Innocent%20people%20suffer%20because%20of%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20many%20governments%20insisting%20on%20putting%20an%20end%20to%20the%20cases%20of%20moral%20policing%2C%20such%20atrocities%20continue%20to%20plague%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Minister%20Ramalinga%20Reddy%20in%20October%20last%20year%20accused%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20workers%20of%20indulging%20in%20%26quot%3Bmischievous%20acts%20in%20disguise%26quot%3B%20and%20alleged%20that%20they%20create%20rifts%20and%20instigate%20communal%20violence%20in%20the%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20supports%20moral%20policing%2C%20fomenting%20tension%2C%20and%20they%20are%20behind%20incidents%20of%20assaults%20and%20communal%20violence.%20%26quot%3BBJP%20workers%20in%20disguise%20--by%20changing%20their%20appearance%20and%20name%20--%20indulge%20in%20mischief.%20It%20is%20their%20nature%20by%20birth%2C%20it%20is%20in%20their%20blood%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Reddy%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20statements%20evoked%20a%20sharp%20reaction%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20whose%20leaders%20termed%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%26quot%3B%20aimed%20at%20covering%20up%20the%20government's%20failure.%20Senior%20BJP%20leader%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Basavaraj%20Bommai%20said%20Mr%20Reddy's%20statement%20is%20%26quot%3Btotally%20mischievous%20and%20misleading%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704717960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fic61pt_karnataka-moral-policing_625x300_08_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fkarnataka-belagavi-moral-policing-inter-faith-cousins-thrashed-with-rods-for-sitting-together-in-karnataka-4823088%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20shocking%20case%20of%20moral%20policing%2C%20a%20man%20and%20woman%20from%20different%20communities%20were%20brutally%20thrashed%20with%20pipes%20and%20rods%20by%20a%20group%20of%2017%20people%20for%20sitting%20together%20near%20a%20lake%20in%20Karnataka's%20Belagavi%20Saturday.%20The%20victims%20happen%20to%20be%20cousins.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fkarnataka-belagavi-moral-policing-inter-faith-cousins-thrashed-with-rods-for-sitting-together-in-karnataka-4823088%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fkarnataka-belagavi-moral-policing-inter-faith-cousins-thrashed-with-rods-for-sitting-together-in-karnataka-4823088%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fkarnataka-belagavi-moral-policing-inter-faith-cousins-thrashed-with-rods-for-sitting-together-in-karnataka-4823088%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNature%20Of%20Violence%20Has%20Changed...%26quot%3B%3A%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%20To%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20nature%20of%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20has%20shifted%20from%20clashes%20between%20two%20communities%20to%20attacks%20by%20insurgents%20on%20security%20forces%20now%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comments%20come%20amid%20fierce%20gunfights%20between%20the%20security%20forces%20and%20insurgents%20in%20Moreh%2C%20a%20key%20trading%20town%20on%20the%20India-Myanmar%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20these%20past%20eight%20months%2C%20unwanted%20incidents%20took%20place%20on%20some%20days%2C%20not%20for%20the%20whole%20eight%20months.%20Three-four%20months%20were%20peaceful%20and%20silent.%20The%20violence%20during%20the%20new%20year%20was%20between%20the%20state%20security%20forces%20and%20militants%2C%20not%20between%20two%20communities.%20Now%2C%20the%20dimension%20of%20the%20conflict%20has%20changed%20to%20state%20forces%20fighting%20against%20militants%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuki%20tribes%20have%20asked%20the%20Centre%20to%20remove%20the%20state%20police%20from%20Moreh%20and%20keep%20only%20central%20forces.%20They%20have%20alleged%20the%20police%20of%20attacking%20Kuki%20civilians.%20The%20Manipur%20Police%20have%20refuted%20the%20allegations%20and%20said%20those%20attacking%20the%20state%20police%20commandos%20were%20hill-based%20insurgents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20called%20for%20ending%20the%20Free-Movement%20Regime%20(FMR)%20on%20the%20India-Myanmar%20border%2C%20which%20allows%20people%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20border%20to%20travel%20over%2015%20km%20without%20papers%20in%20each%20other's%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBorder%20fencing%20is%20a%20must.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20cancel%20the%20FMR.%20Of%20course%2C%20people%20should%20come.%20Follow%20the%20rules%2C%20get%20paperwork%20as%20is%20done%20in%20any%20international%20travel.%20But%20right%20now%20there%20is%20no%20system%20in%20place%2C%20no%20checks%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20said%20they%20suspect%20the%20involvement%20of%20foreign%20mercenaries%20in%20the%20Manipur%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20what%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20been%20doing%20to%20restore%20full%20normalcy%20in%20Manipur%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPeople%20in%20the%20hills%20and%20the%20valley%20are%20themselves%20trying%20to%20restore%20peace.%20From%20the%20government%20side%20also%20we%20are%20trying%20our%20best%20with%20the%20guidance%20of%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah.%20Both%20sides%20have%20been%20talking%20and%20discussions%20happening%20through%20proper%20channels.%20I%20can't%20disclose%20everything.%20Total%20normalcy%20will%20be%20restored%20very%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20government%20will%20give%20Rs%201%20lakh%20each%20to%20all%20displaced%20people%20in%2010%20days%20so%20that%20they%20can%20meet%20their%20immediate%20expenditure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20blamed%20several%20successive%20governments%20in%20the%20past%20for%20the%20current%20crisis.%20%26quot%3BHad%20the%20leaders%20back%20in%201947-49%20during%20the%20merger%20given%20some%20attention%2C%20this%20problem%20would%20not%20have%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20border%20is%20398%20km%20long.%20Some%20people%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20border%20share%20some%20ethnic%20ties.%20Had%20the%20fencing%20been%20done%20well%20decades%20ago%20and%20a%20pass%20system%20developed%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20influx%20would%20not%20have%20grown%20so%20big.%20The%20Centre%20in%20those%20early%20years%20left%20Manipur%20on%20its%20own.%20The%20border%20is%20guarded%20by%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20but%20they%20are%20doing%20two%20jobs%20-%20guarding%20the%20border%20and%20carrying%20out%20counter-insurgency%20operations.%20They%20are%20stationed%2010-20%20km%20inside%20from%20the%20border.%20On%20top%20of%20this%2C%20there%20is%20the%20Free-Movement%20Regime%20(FMR)%2C%20which%20allows%20people%20from%20across%20the%20border%20to%20come%20for%20several%20kilometres%20without%20any%20checks.%20So%20think%2C%20they%20are%20the%20same%20tribe%2C%20same%20community%2C%20same%20language%2C%20same%20culture%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20ever%20thought%20about%20the%20indigenous%20people%20of%20Manipur%2C%20no%20one.%20It%20is%20only%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20came%20that%20we%20saw%20development%20and%20security%20in%20this%20region.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20previous%20governments%20-%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20say%20about%20other%20states%20-%20left%20Manipur%20on%20its%20own.%20Whatever%20is%20happening%20now%20is%20because%20of%20the%20inaction%20by%20the%20previous%20governments%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20180%20have%20died%20and%20thousands%20have%20been%20internally%20displaced%20in%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20that%20began%20on%20May%203%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704717900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fi8jpm8o8_n-biren-singh-ndtv_625x300_08_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnature-of-violence-changed-to-security-forces-vs-insurgents-manipur-chief-minister-n-biren-singh-to-ndtv-4823360%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20nature%20of%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20has%20shifted%20from%20clashes%20between%20two%20communities%20to%20attacks%20by%20insurgents%20on%20security%20forces%20now%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnature-of-violence-changed-to-security-forces-vs-insurgents-manipur-chief-minister-n-biren-singh-to-ndtv-4823360%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnature-of-violence-changed-to-security-forces-vs-insurgents-manipur-chief-minister-n-biren-singh-to-ndtv-4823360%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%