a.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FYoutubers-at-Tulsi-Village-Raipur_11zon-1704460010-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-337622%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20YouTubers%20of%20Tulsi%20village%2C%20Raipur.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInitial%20hiccups%20and%20successes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Jay%20and%20Gyanendra%E2%80%99s%20families%20have%20still%20not%20completely%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20their%20YouTube%20careers.%20They%20do%20not%20look%20at%20what%20they%20do%20as%20something%20which%20will%20give%20them%20security.%20Initially%2C%20both%20of%20them%20were%20criticised%20a%20lot%20by%20their%20family%20members%20to%20have%20left%20%E2%80%98better%E2%80%99%20jobs%20for%20YouTube.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20beginning%2C%20we%20gained%202-3%20thousand%20subscribers%20within%20a%20month.%20Our%20videos%20were%20circulating%20on%20WhatsApp%2C%20which%20was%20a%20significant%20help.%20We%20used%20to%20create%20short%20videos%2C%20often%20without%20much%20understanding%2C%20preparation%2C%20or%20ideas.%20Now%2C%20we%20have%201%2C20%2C000%20subscribers%20on%20our%20channel%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Gyanendra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20first%20wish%20was%20to%20make%20movies.%20Our%20goal%20was%20to%20do%20something%20that%20could%20provide%20employment%20to%20all%20the%20villages.%20We%20wanted%20to%20work%20on%20all%20online%20projects%20with%20the%20youth%20from%20our%20village.%20Our%20village%20is%20a%20small%20film%20city.%20Here%2C%20everyone%20is%20an%20artist%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%20with%20happiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20women%2C%20the%20elderly%2C%20and%20the%20children%2C%20all%20take%20an%20interest%20in%20our%20videos%20and%20support%20us.%20There%20are%20hundreds%20of%20YouTubers.%20We%20have%20all%20kinds%20of%20locations%20available%20in%20our%20village%20to%20tell%20a%2