com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjute-root-3-1704377063-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-337529%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20jute%20products%20have%20demand%20in%20India%20as%20well%20as%20abroad.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Chaitali%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20noticed%20a%20police%20van%20with%20people%20disembarking%2C%20hands%20restrained%20with%20handcuffs%20and%20a%20thick%20rope%20around%20their%20waists%20%E2%80%93%20the%20customary%20way%20the%20accused%20were%20brought%20to%20the%20courtroom%20in%20those%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20my%20curiosity%20peaked%2C%20I%20approached%20one%20of%20my%20dad%E2%80%99s%20colleagues%20and%20asked%20who%20he%20was.%20Labelled%20as%20wrongdoers%2C%20they%20were%20being%20taken%20to%20the%20courtroom%20to%20face%20the%20consequences.%20I%20stood%20there%2C%20observing%20them%2C%20while%20their%20family%20members%20rushed%20towards%20them%2C%20engaging%20in%20fervent%20conversations%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20family%20members%E2%80%99%20suffering%2C%20little%20Chaitali%20felt%20like%20she%20should%20do%20something%20for%20them.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20too%20young%20but%20I%20had%20made%20up%20my%20mind%20that%20I%20want%20to%20do%20something%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20age%2C%20Chaitali%20decided%20she%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20social%20worker%20and%20chose%20the%20path%20of%20helping%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETaking%20Jute%20To%20the%20Global%20Stage%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20after%20several%20years%20of%20working%20with%20various%20NGOs%2C%20Chaitali%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20the%20Rakshak%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20focuses%20on%20empowering%20male%20and%20female%20inmates%20and%20other%20underprivileged%20women.%