2%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShe%20has%20also%20trained%203000%20inmates%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20government.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Chaitali%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20India%2C%20especially%20in%20Bengal%2C%20the%20jute%20industry%20involves%20approximately%2040%20lakh%20people.%20We%20have%20actively%20engaged%20inmates%20in%20crafting%20jute%20products%2C%20showcasing%20their%20creations%20at%20various%20locations%2C%20including%20different%20chambers%20and%20events%20on%20both%20national%20and%20international%20platforms%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20train%20and%20incubate%20these%20inmates%2C%20she%20connected%20with%20the%20National%20Jute%20Board%20of%20India%20(NJB).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20training%20program%20spans%2045%20days%2C%20and%20we%20are%20proud%20to%20have%20partnered%20with%20NJB%20for%20its%20successful%20implementation.%20Our%20initial%20accomplishment%20was%20the%20training%20conducted%20at%20the%20Dandam%20Central%20Correctional%20Home%2C%20benefiting%20the%20prisoners%20there.%20Subsequently%2C%20I%20extended%20the%20initiative%20by%20providing%20additional%20training%2C%20leading%20to%20continued%20production%20and%20participation%20in%20various%20exhibitions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20promote%20acceptance%20and%20usage%2C%20the%20organisation%20implemented%20a%20practice%20of%20free%20gifting%20initially.%20This%20strategy%20aims%20to%20introduce%20people%20to%20the%20products%2C%20fostering%20acceptance%20and%20encouraging%20reuse%20in%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20this%20project%2C%20we%20have%20trained%20about%203%2C000%20inmates%20in%20making%20jute%20products.%20This%20project%20has%20evolved%20into%20%E2%80%98Root%20to%20Jute%E2%80%99.%20Notably%2C%20it%20has%20been%20incubated%20by%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn